38:14.625 --> 38:16.125
-Hey!
-Hey.

38:17.083 --> 38:19.458
What's up, guys? Is it a hit or what?

38:24.000 --> 38:26.416
When the speakers are blasting

38:26.500 --> 38:28.083
They lose their minds

38:28.166 --> 38:31.625
"A hit or what," Doni?
It's the hit of the summer.

38:31.708 --> 38:33.875
Hey, keep that passport handy.

38:34.375 --> 38:36.708
-We're going to Europe.
-Europe?

38:38.375 --> 38:40.791
London, Paris, and Lisbon.

38:40.875 --> 38:42.333
To start off.

38:42.416 --> 38:44.833
-But keep working hard!
-Alright.

38:44.916 --> 38:48.333
Keep dreaming big. No one can stop you.

38:50.916 --> 38:52.375
Off to Europe, then!

38:52.458 --> 38:54.625
-Let's hear it for him!
-Thank you.

38:54.708 --> 38:56.208
Tough kid.

38:56.291 --> 38:59.000
We did it. We did it, man.

38:59.583 --> 39:01.583
Do you know why we called you?

39:01.666 --> 39:05.333
Our congregation will sponsor
the candidacy of a young member

39:05.416 --> 39:07.875
to represent us at City Council.

39:07.958 --> 39:09.250
Yes, Levi.

39:09.750 --> 39:12.875
Pastor Leopoldo and I
talked to the party's strategist

39:12.958 --> 39:14.583
about voting prospects.

39:14.666 --> 39:17.291
He saw the huge appeal you have,

39:17.375 --> 39:19.625
especially among the youth.

39:20.125 --> 39:21.458
I'll get to the point.

39:22.041 --> 39:25.000
Pastor Val and I invite you,
on behalf of our church,

39:25.083 --> 39:28.583
to launch you
as a potential candidate for City Council.

39:28.666 --> 39:30.958
Sure, we need to prepare you.

39:31.041 --> 39:33.958
It's a process,
but I want to know what you think.

39:34.041 --> 39:37.291
I know this invitation
seems out of the blue,

39:37.833 --> 39:40.208
but we've been eyeing you for a while.

39:40.708 --> 39:42.000
You're just the right fit.

39:45.458 --> 39:46.291
Well,

39:47.041 --> 39:48.333
I'm speechless.

39:55.875 --> 39:56.833
Excuse me.

39:56.916 --> 39:59.333
So, was it like you imagined?

39:59.416 --> 40:00.916
-You knew?
-Of course.

40:01.000 --> 40:02.291
Look at you!

40:03.041 --> 40:04.250
Listen,

40:05.500 --> 40:07.541
I'll tell my parents
about us this week, okay?

40:08.416 --> 40:11.541
Especially now, their approval
will mean a lot to me.

40:13.125 --> 40:14.708
I need to talk to you.

40:14.791 --> 40:15.916
Go ahead.

40:16.000 --> 40:18.791
I spent more than I should
in the inauguration.

40:19.333 --> 40:20.750
I know, Rita.

40:21.708 --> 40:23.708
-Do your parents know?
-Yes.

40:23.791 --> 40:26.166
Tell them I'm gonna pay it.

40:26.750 --> 40:29.208
I mean it. I won't let the church pay.

40:29.291 --> 40:30.333
What do you mean?

40:30.833 --> 40:32.041
It's been paid.

40:32.125 --> 40:34.916
Someone made a donation
specifically for that.

40:35.916 --> 40:36.750
Who?

40:37.416 --> 40:38.625
It was anonymous, but clear.

40:39.208 --> 40:40.958
"To pay for the party."

41:15.416 --> 41:16.583
-What's up?
-Hey.

41:16.666 --> 41:17.875
-All good?
-Yeah.

41:18.375 --> 41:20.333
-Hey, man.
-What's up, bro?

41:20.416 --> 41:21.750
How are you, Jaspion?

41:22.875 --> 41:24.083
You know,

41:24.916 --> 41:26.083
missing him.

41:27.666 --> 41:29.541
-You know how it is.
-Yeah.

41:30.416 --> 41:33.375
It's tough, man.
But you're right. Don't stop.

41:34.583 --> 41:36.458
Rivaldo wanted it to succeed.

41:43.458 --> 41:45.750
How about Luzi? Pumping out hits?

41:45.833 --> 41:47.708
She came to help me out.

41:48.291 --> 41:51.583
At least I parted ways
with my old manager.

41:51.666 --> 41:53.875
-You did?
-I had to.

41:53.958 --> 41:55.875
Let's go see Luan, then.

41:56.458 --> 41:58.041
We'll work together again?

41:58.625 --> 42:01.458
If he manages your career with me, sure.

42:02.416 --> 42:05.333
When I return from Europe,
we'll sort this out.

42:05.416 --> 42:06.333
Deal.

42:06.416 --> 42:08.333
Do you have time for me?

42:08.416 --> 42:09.375
Right now.

42:09.458 --> 42:11.375
No, I do the scheduling.

42:11.458 --> 42:13.791
Cancel the next three. I'll be a while.

42:25.625 --> 42:28.833
It's just another step
in everything you've been doing.

42:29.666 --> 42:31.166
Just look at this church.

42:32.500 --> 42:35.333
Everything's working out
better than ever for me.

42:35.416 --> 42:37.083
What a blessing!

42:37.166 --> 42:38.708
The church's opening.

42:39.333 --> 42:41.291
The debt being paid off.

42:41.375 --> 42:43.708
This unexpected offer.

42:43.791 --> 42:44.875
Even Levi.

42:45.916 --> 42:47.166
I don't know, Pastor.

42:47.916 --> 42:49.250
I'm not sure I deserve it.

42:49.333 --> 42:51.333
Rita, haven't you earned it?

42:52.500 --> 42:53.416
So…

42:55.166 --> 42:57.833
Now, let's welcome people to church?

42:57.916 --> 42:59.041
Yes!

43:09.791 --> 43:12.666
I got rid of everything
that tied me to it.

43:12.750 --> 43:15.750
I want to find Jesus. It might not work…

43:15.833 --> 43:17.666
It's working, Formiga.

43:19.166 --> 43:21.291
-It was you, right?
-Me what?

43:21.375 --> 43:24.041
"To pay for the party
of Vila Áurea's church."

43:29.166 --> 43:30.958
Looking good in the picture?

43:31.041 --> 43:32.833
It's great, man.

43:35.333 --> 43:38.000
Hold up! I take care of the talent.

43:39.083 --> 43:40.791
We're going international.

43:40.875 --> 43:42.125
That's right, kid!

43:42.208 --> 43:43.916
-We made it.
-We did.

43:44.000 --> 43:45.916
I knew you'd go places.

43:49.458 --> 43:51.416
-What do you want?
-The float.

43:51.500 --> 43:52.625
The pink float!

43:52.708 --> 43:54.375
Is that what you want?

43:54.458 --> 43:55.500
No hands!

43:56.000 --> 43:58.750
Swim this way. Come!

43:59.416 --> 44:01.625
Swim this way.

44:01.708 --> 44:03.458
Such a princess!

44:03.541 --> 44:06.416
What's up, everyone?
Here to give a message.

44:06.500 --> 44:08.666
My first European tour is coming up.

44:08.750 --> 44:11.708
I'll perform in London, Paris, and Lisbon.

44:11.791 --> 44:14.208
Come in hot, and get ready!

44:16.041 --> 44:18.500
Hello, boys. Have you seen Levi?

44:19.458 --> 44:20.708
Oh, thanks.

44:27.625 --> 44:30.125
-Hey. Did you want to see me?
-Yes.

44:30.208 --> 44:32.041
I have ideas for the campaign.

44:34.666 --> 44:35.833
Have a seat, please.

44:51.750 --> 44:52.791
Rita…

44:57.083 --> 44:59.083
God revealed a prophecy to my mom.

45:04.333 --> 45:05.583
She saw that…

45:08.750 --> 45:10.708
my future is not with you.

45:17.083 --> 45:18.041
I'm sorry.

45:22.500 --> 45:23.541
I can't do anything.

45:30.083 --> 45:31.000
Levi…

45:33.791 --> 45:35.416
I know that prophecy.

45:38.916 --> 45:42.416
She'd never want her prince
to get involved with a nobody.

45:43.000 --> 45:43.833
Right?

46:10.458 --> 46:11.375
What's this?

46:12.208 --> 46:13.166
What's in here?

46:13.958 --> 46:15.125
Baby.

46:15.208 --> 46:16.583
Baby!

46:16.666 --> 46:18.166
Nice house, brother!

46:18.250 --> 46:20.250
-You like it?
-Damn.

46:20.333 --> 46:22.166
-Awesome!
-Hey!

46:23.166 --> 46:25.833
Look who is here!

46:25.916 --> 46:28.208
Bringing some life into this place.

46:28.291 --> 46:30.166
You're glowing, Scheyla!

46:30.250 --> 46:32.125
Thanks! How are you, Ritinha?

46:32.208 --> 46:34.000
How much time is left?

46:34.083 --> 46:35.875
We're almost there.

46:35.958 --> 46:37.708
-Hey. All good?
-You're okay?

46:38.291 --> 46:40.166
-You're doing well, man.
-You know it.

46:41.541 --> 46:44.791
Could we imagine such a place
when we were kids? Never.

46:44.875 --> 46:46.833
I did, but we weren't in it.

46:48.666 --> 46:49.958
But I'll be honest.

46:50.041 --> 46:52.625
I never imagined you'd be a star,

46:52.708 --> 46:54.166
and you'd be a politician.

46:54.250 --> 46:56.041
That's how I like it!

46:56.125 --> 46:57.375
How's Bruninha doing?

46:57.458 --> 46:59.333
She won't leave the pool.

46:59.416 --> 47:01.000
She's like a little fish.

47:01.083 --> 47:03.166
Just try to get her out of there.

47:03.666 --> 47:04.500
I can imagine.

47:05.125 --> 47:06.916
Have you picked a name already?

47:07.708 --> 47:08.666
Tell her.

47:08.750 --> 47:11.833
We haven't chosen a name.
We chose something else.

47:12.833 --> 47:14.625
Scheyla and I were talking.

47:15.208 --> 47:17.125
We'd like you to be the godparents.

47:17.208 --> 47:19.250
-I can't believe it, Nando!
-For real?

47:19.333 --> 47:20.791
-Sure!
-Give me a hug.

47:21.625 --> 47:23.000
-I'm so happy, Scheyla!
-Yeah, bro.

47:23.833 --> 47:26.083
I told you he'd tear up.

47:28.416 --> 47:30.166
What do you want for lunch?

47:30.666 --> 47:32.458
It depends on who's cooking.

47:32.541 --> 47:34.416
Just ask the cook to make it.

47:34.500 --> 47:38.375
Well, in that case,
we have a special order for you.

47:38.458 --> 47:40.500
-Oh no.
-Don't give me that look.

47:40.583 --> 47:43.125
You want pizza at this hour?

47:43.208 --> 47:44.375
Who remembers it?

47:44.458 --> 47:45.833
This pizza is dope

47:45.916 --> 47:47.375
Pepperoni and mozzarella

47:47.458 --> 47:49.791
People say it's the best in the favela

47:49.875 --> 47:52.250
Delivery guy done goofed
We went for it

47:52.333 --> 47:54.500
The pizza is good, and Nando has arrived

47:54.583 --> 47:56.250
And Nando has arrived

47:57.666 --> 47:59.583
-I almost forgot.
-Daddy!

48:00.125 --> 48:02.750
For real, what do you want to eat?

48:02.833 --> 48:04.000
Daddy.

48:05.083 --> 48:06.083
Daddy.

48:08.291 --> 48:09.416
Nando!

48:09.500 --> 48:11.458
-We can't have pizza?
-Nando!

48:18.000 --> 48:22.041
The police have tracked down
the criminal and his link to the gang.

48:22.125 --> 48:25.583
This criminal, known as Nando from VA,

48:25.666 --> 48:28.208
is considered one of those responsible

48:28.291 --> 48:32.458
for various crimes related
to drug trafficking and even murder.

48:32.541 --> 48:36.666
A guy like this
should rot in jail for good!

48:36.750 --> 48:38.333
Show him on the screen.

48:38.416 --> 48:41.291
DANGEROUS CRIMINAL
WANTED FOR MURDER AND TRAFFICKING

48:43.583 --> 48:45.708
Your boss doesn't know your name.

48:46.208 --> 48:47.208
I don't care.

48:48.041 --> 48:49.875
Everyone will know who I am.

53:04.083 --> 53:07.833
Subtitle translation by: Jonathan Williams
